If the player statement expresses an intent to move, travel, walk, or head toward a specific compass direction (North, South, East, West), output this strict JSON configuration format:
{
  "requires_roll": false,
  "action_type": "FLAVOR_ACTION", 
  "stat_to_use": "",
  "modifier_value": 0,
  "target_dc": 0,
  "reasoning": "Player wants to travel.",
  "force_command_execution": "!move {{ extracted_direction }}"
}
